Veba plans to grow telecoms further in 97 . German diversified utility group Veba AG said on Wednesday that it would continue to expand its telecommunications operations with its partner , utility RWE AG . The joint venture , which was founded in October with RWE , plans in 1997 to offer telephone service to private subscribers . " We have set the ambitious goal of becoming the premier private carrier in the German telecommunications market , " Ulrich Hartmann , Veba ' s management board chairman , said in the text of a speech to be delivered at a news conference . Veba said that last year its E - plus mobile telecommunications service brought its customer base up to 500 , 000 subscribers , more than doubling the previous year ' s figure . - - Clifford Coonan , Frankfurt Newsroom + 49 69 756525 
